'''DevMountain''' is a private [[coding bootcamp]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.coursereport.com/schools/devmountain|title=Course Report: DevMountain|date=2016|website=Course Report|quote=Founded in 2013, DevMountain is a coding school in with various locations providing software engineering and tech education, career placement services, and a lifelong community of professional and like-minded individuals.|accessdate=6 November 2016}}</ref> school that offers in-person and online courses ranging from 6 to 26 weeks in a variety of subjects including [[web development]], mobile programming, user experience design, software quality assurance, and salesforce development. The school was founded in [[Provo, Utah]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://techcrunch.com/2017/05/03/candy/|title=Inside DevMountain’s sweet code school|publisher=TechCrunch|date=2017-05-03}}</ref> by Cahlan Sharp, Tyler Richards, and Colt Henrie in 2013.<ref name=founders>{{cite news|last1=Romero|first1=Sarah|title=BYU grad brings 12-week developer coding school to Provo|url=http://universe.byu.edu/2013/08/01/byu-grad-brings-12-week-developer-coding-school-to-provo/|accessdate=6 November 2016|work=The Daily Universe|date=1 Aug 2013|location=Provo, UT}}</ref> DevMountain provides free housing to its full-time students for the length of the program to help them accommodate long hours of work.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bizjournals.com/dallas/news/2016/09/15/exclusive-coding-school-in-downtown-dallas-doubles.html|title=exclusive-coding-school-in-downtown-dallas-doubles|website=bizjournals.com|access-date=2017-10-24}}</ref>

As of August 2017, DevMountain has four campus locations in Salt Lake City, Utah, Provo, Utah, Dallas, Texas, and Phoenix, Arizona.

In April 2016, the software engineering school, DevMountain was acquired by [[Capella Education Company]] for $20 million.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bizjournals.com/twincities/news/2016/05/04/capella-buys-dev-mountain-coding-school.html|title=capella-buys-dev-mountain-coding-school|website=bizjournals.com|access-date=2017-10-24}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20160504006705/en/Capella-Acquisition-DevMountain-Extends-Leadership-Position-Job-Ready|title=Capella Acquisition of DevMountain Extends Leadership Position in Job-Ready Skills Market {{!}} Business Wire|website=www.businesswire.com|access-date=2016-11-09}}</ref>

